07:32.000 --> 07:36.000
what with

07:32.000 --> 07:36.000
your writing and directing

07:32.000 --> 07:36.000
and assistant-managing.

07:36.000 --> 07:39.000
I would never dream

07:36.000 --> 07:39.000
of wasting your time.

07:39.000 --> 07:42.000
Trust me, this will be

07:39.000 --> 07:42.000
more than worth it.

07:46.000 --> 07:48.000
Okay, let's go.

07:48.000 --> 07:50.000
Let's go.

07:52.000 --> 07:53.000
Here?

07:53.000 --> 07:55.000
On aisle three?

07:55.000 --> 07:57.000
I assume you've prepared

07:55.000 --> 07:57.000
a monologue.

07:57.000 --> 07:59.000
Of course.

08:06.000 --> 08:07.000
[exhales]

08:11.000 --> 08:13.000
I can't bear it.

08:14.000 --> 08:17.000
They're so young and beautiful.

08:17.000 --> 08:19.000
Why did they ever

08:17.000 --> 08:19.000
have to get old?

08:21.000 --> 08:24.000
Mama, I'm here.

08:24.000 --> 08:26.000
I'm grown-up.

08:27.000 --> 08:28.000
[moaning]

08:32.000 --> 08:34.000
[baby crying]

08:34.000 --> 08:35.000
Mama.

08:37.000 --> 08:39.000
Just... look at me.

08:39.000 --> 08:41.000
[object breaks]

08:41.000 --> 08:43.000
One minute...

08:43.000 --> 08:44.000
-[man over PA]

08:43.000 --> 08:44.000
Clean-up on aisle five.

08:43.000 --> 08:44.000
-...like you really saw me.

08:45.000 --> 08:46.000
[baby continues crying]

08:46.000 --> 08:49.000
I'm sorry.

08:46.000 --> 08:49.000
Sorry, could we just try again?

08:49.000 --> 08:51.000
-[man over PA]

08:49.000 --> 08:51.000
Mickey, price check, aisle six.

08:49.000 --> 08:51.000
-That's me, hon.

08:51.000 --> 08:52.000
[sighs]

