And this psycho shit's

10:07.000 --> 10:11.000
your idea for me

10:07.000 --> 10:11.000
to become more human?

10:11.000 --> 10:12.000
No. God, no.

10:12.000 --> 10:15.000
That sketch, all of those

10:12.000 --> 10:15.000
sketches are just musings.

10:15.000 --> 10:19.000
Bad ideas,

10:15.000 --> 10:19.000
excrement that I have to...

10:19.000 --> 10:22.000
pass before I can

10:19.000 --> 10:22.000
hopefully lay the golden egg.

10:22.000 --> 10:23.000
Is this just a trick?

10:24.000 --> 10:26.000
