My dad put them in

16:18.000 --> 16:21.000
during my first surgery. Why?

16:23.000 --> 16:26.000
Chief thinks he could

16:23.000 --> 16:26.000
rebuild my sense of touch.

16:26.000 --> 16:27.000
Congratulations, man.

16:27.000 --> 16:29.000
He also said

16:27.000 --> 16:29.000
it would take decades.

16:29.000 --> 16:32.000
Which would be fine

16:29.000 --> 16:32.000
if he wasn't dying.

16:32.000 --> 16:34.000
Niles always finds a way.

16:35.000 --> 16:37.000
You know who else always

16:35.000 --> 16:37.000
finds a way and isn't dying?

16:37.000 --> 16:39.000
Your dad.

