You know how they say

16:40.000 --> 16:42.000
the longer you're away

16:40.000 --> 16:42.000
from people,

16:42.000 --> 16:45.000
the harder it is to remember

16:42.000 --> 16:45.000
what they look like?

16:45.000 --> 16:48.000
Well, I have that

16:45.000 --> 16:48.000
but with sensations.

16:48.000 --> 16:54.000
I used to hold my arm out

16:48.000 --> 16:54.000
when it was raining,

16:48.000 --> 16:54.000
feeling the drops hit my skin.

16:54.000 --> 16:56.000
I remember doing that,

16:56.000 --> 16:57.000
but not the feeling.

16:58.000 --> 17:01.000
Running my hands

16:58.000 --> 17:01.000
through my wife's hair.

17:01.000 --> 17:05.000
In my head,

17:01.000 --> 17:05.000
I know it felt amazing,

17:05.000 --> 17:08.000
but I don't know

17:05.000 --> 17:08.000
at the same time.

17:08.000 --> 17:09.000
[sighs]

17:09.000 --> 17:11.000
It's all floating away from me.

17:37.000 --> 17:38.000
Hey.

17:39.000 --> 17:41.000
