17:50.000 --> 17:51.000
Dex...

17:52.000 --> 17:55.000
this is Larry Trainor,

17:52.000 --> 17:55.000
your grandfather.

17:56.000 --> 17:57.000
Wow.

17:58.000 --> 18:00.000
