25:10.000 --> 25:14.000
This is an opportunity, Larry.

25:14.000 --> 25:16.000
For you to air

25:14.000 --> 25:16.000
your dirty laundry.

25:16.000 --> 25:19.000
Express your love,

25:16.000 --> 25:19.000
