25:24.000 --> 25:27.000
[Dex] I'm gonna get you.

25:24.000 --> 25:27.000
I gonna get you.

25:27.000 --> 25:29.000
-Get him, get him.

25:27.000 --> 25:29.000
-[Paul] Oh, no.

25:29.000 --> 25:30.000
