33:10.000 --> 33:14.000
Would it have killed her

33:10.000 --> 33:14.000
to let me start

33:10.000 --> 33:14.000
my monologue over?

33:14.000 --> 33:16.000
I'm sorry.

33:16.000 --> 33:18.000
Hey, bud, you like

33:16.000 --> 33:18.000
char on your dog? Yeah?

33:18.000 --> 33:21.000
Oh, who am I kidding,

33:18.000 --> 33:21.000
I could've started 1,000 times

33:18.000 --> 33:21.000
and I still would've collapsed.

33:21.000 --> 33:23.000
Wanted it too badly.

33:23.000 --> 33:27.000
To prove to Mother that

33:23.000 --> 33:27.000
I could land a role on my own

33:23.000 --> 33:27.000
and when I want something,

33:27.000 --> 33:31.000
that's when that tumor

33:27.000 --> 33:31.000
of a thought

33:27.000 --> 33:31.000
bursts into my mind.

33:31.000 --> 33:33.000
You, uh...

33:31.000 --> 33:33.000
You close with your mom?

33:34.000 --> 33:35.000
God, no.

33:38.000 --> 33:40.000
That witch died ages ago.

33:40.000 --> 33:42.000
But she haunts me.

33:42.000 --> 33:46.000
The things she did,

33:42.000 --> 33:46.000
they haunt me.

33:48.000 --> 33:50.000
Yeah. Uh...

33:50.000 --> 33:52.000
Oops, I, uh,

33:50.000 --> 33:52.000
forgot the ketchup.

33:52.000 --> 33:53.000
Excuse me.

33:59.000 --> 34:01.000
[door closes]

34:01.000 --> 34:05.000
Your father seems nice enough,

34:01.000 --> 34:05.000
and I'm sure he means well.

34:05.000 --> 34:09.000
But don't ever let him

34:05.000 --> 34:09.000
crush your spirit

34:05.000 --> 34:09.000
and step on your dreams.

