46:37.000 --> 46:39.000
[gasping in fear]

46:39.000 --> 46:41.000
No, no, no. Stop. Stop it!

46:41.000 --> 46:43.000
No! Stop, stop, stop!

46:43.000 --> 46:44.000
Stop!

46:44.000 --> 46:45.000
[Manny growling]

46:49.000 --> 46:50.000
[screeching]

46:51.000 --> 46:53.000
[screeching in pain]

46:53.000 --> 46:54.000
[Dorothy] Manny!

46:56.000 --> 46:57.000
Manny!

46:59.000 --> 47:02.000
[Candlemaker]

46:59.000 --> 47:02.000
Our friend is dead.

47:03.000 --> 47:04.000
[Dorothy sobbing]

47:04.000 --> 47:06.000
Manny!

47:06.000 --> 47:08.000
[Candlemaker]  Make a wish.

47:10.000 --> 47:13.000
[sobbing]

47:10.000 --> 47:13.000
Dorothy, I'm sorry.

47:18.000 --> 47:20.000
[sniffles]

