47:28.000 --> 47:30.000
[blows]

47:31.000 --> 47:32.000
[train running]

47:36.000 --> 47:37.000
[crashing]

47:37.000 --> 47:38.000
[rattling]

47:52.000 --> 47:54.000
[Candlemaker growling]

47:58.000 --> 47:59.000
[groans]

48:01.000 --> 48:04.000
He's coming!

48:01.000 --> 48:04.000
Don't let him get me!

48:04.000 --> 48:06.000
-[screaming]

48:04.000 --> 48:06.000
-Baby Doll.

48:07.000 --> 48:08.000
[Candlemaker growling]

48:11.000 --> 48:12.000
Get back.

48:12.000 --> 48:13.000
[electricity crackling]

48:14.000 --> 48:16.000
Let's get out of here.

48:18.000 --> 48:19.000
I'm sorry!

48:19.000 --> 48:22.000
It's okay. It's okay.

48:19.000 --> 48:22.000
Everything's gonna be okay.

48:19.000 --> 48:22.000
Come, come.

48:24.000 --> 48:26.000
[Candlemaker growling]

48:27.000 --> 48:29.000
Get out of here.

48:27.000 --> 48:29.000
This isn't your job.

48:29.000 --> 48:30.000
Hammerhead, no!

48:32.000 --> 48:34.000
Come at us, you fucking fuck!

48:35.000 --> 48:36.000
[Candlemaker roars]

48:39.000 --> 48:40.000
[gasps]

48:44.000 --> 48:46.000
[Candlemaker snarling]

48:46.000 --> 48:48.000
[Hammerhead groans]

48:48.000 --> 48:51.000
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

48:51.000 --> 48:53.000
I didn't mean to!

